high_descs: Turn left, walk towards wall, turn right and walk to counter with apple on it.
Pick up closest knife.
Turn right walk towards wall turn left to the counter with bread on it.
Slice the loaf of bread on the counter.
Put knife on top of the loaf of bread.
Pick of the slice of bread.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Put bread on the bottom shelf of the fridge, close door, open fridge door and get bread from fridge.
Turn right, walk to counter with apple on it.
Place bread on counter next to apple.
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of bread, put bread in fridge, remove bread from fridge, place on counter next to apple.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight, then turn right to go to the counter between the stove and the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter, and to the left of the apple.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left to face the counter to the right to the stove.
Slice the bread on the counter.
Put the knife on the counter, next to the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn left, go forward, then turn right to face the fridge.
Chill the slice of bread inside of the fridge.
Turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the counter next to the fridge.
Put the slice of bread on the counter, to the left of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and walk 6 steps, take a right and walk 4 steps and stop.
Pick up the silver knife to the left of the apple.
Turn right for 5 steps, turn left to face the counter.
Slice a chunk of bread off the end of the loaf..
Place the knife on the loaf.
Pick up the sliced chunk of bread from the loaf on the counter, leaving the knife on the loaf.
Turn left, take nine steps, turn right and stop in front of the refrigerator.

Open the bottom refrigerator door, place the bread chunk on the front left of the top shelf, wait a few moments, open the bottom door of the refrigerator and take out the bread chunk on the top shelf.
Take a right for three steps and turn left to face the counter.
Place the  chunk of bread on the counter to the left of the apple with the cut side facing the apple.
anns.task_desc: Place a cut chunk of bread on the counter.
